title: The Most Dangerous Game Master
description: Dr. Wily creates an android that is a replica of Kevin's worst enemy from high school.

title: Videolympics
description: Mother Brain challenges the N-Team to an athletic competition on Mount Icarus, thus distracting them from stopping her from finding the Three Sacred Treasures.

title: Mr. & Mrs. Mother Brain
description: Simon gets shot by a "love-at-first-sight" arrow and falls in love with Mother Brain.

title: Quest for the Potion of Power
The Lost City of Kongoland
description: When the lost city of Kongoland arises after 1000 years, the N-Team goes to investigate. When they arrive, an ancient treasure possesses Princess Lana with the spirit of Konga, the leader of the Konkas.

title: I Wish I Was a Wombatman
The Invasion of the Paper Pedalers
Pursuit of the Magic Hoop
description: In Hoopland, an inventor is annoyed that he is small so he builds a robot and makes a wish, however when the wish goes wrong; Captain N, Princess Lana and Larry Bird help him by going into Hoop Mountain and face Clockman.

title: Return to Castlevania
description: During the Simon Belmont Awards, the Poltergeist King says that Trevor Belmont who is Simon Belmont's grandfather is a coward which makes Simon worried until him and Captain N get advice from a wizard.

title: Totally Tetrisized
description: After playing a riddle game, Captain N, Princess Lana and Simon get a call from Mayor Squaresly that Tetris is in trouble so they go and check it out while the Puzzle King plans to rule Tetris.

title: Battle of the Baseball Know-It-Alls
description: In Baseball World, Captain N is playing baseball with Bo Jackson until Mother Brain kidnaps Princess Lana and warps Captain N, Simon, Duke, Megaman, Kid Icarus and Bo into the cellars. How can they get out and save Lana?

title: A Tale of Two Dogs
description: Captain N and Megaman are in Megaland trying to defeat Topman but when it was defeated, Captain N and Megaman argue which dog was best (Duke or Rush) which gives Dr. Wily an idea to stop the heroes while working on a peace robot.

title: The Fractured Fantasy of Captain N
description: While in Final Fantasy, Captain N is jealous of the Prince who is a friend of Princess Lana until a mysterious "fairy godfather" put Kevin in a spell which Lana, Megaman and Kid Icarus must recover both the Prince and Captain N.
